509
00:44:55,907 --> 00:44:57,033
Ada apa?

510
00:45:04,040 --> 00:45:05,417
Apa maksudmu?

511
00:45:06,459 --> 00:45:07,836
UNIT GAWAT DARURAT

512
00:45:08,503 --> 00:45:09,504
<i>Ini tak bisa diterima.</i>

513
00:45:11,423 --> 00:45:13,174
Aku merawat 100 pasien sehari.

514
00:45:13,842 --> 00:45:16,094
Bahkan saat aku dipukul pasien mabuk

515
00:45:17,679 --> 00:45:20,306
