- Baik.

533
00:46:13,985 --> 00:46:15,320
Di sini.

534
00:46:18,907 --> 00:46:20,325
Satu, dua, tiga.

535
00:46:22,494 --> 00:46:24,287
Tensi 100-60. Denyut 100. Saturasi 95.

536
00:46:24,370 --> 00:46:26,456
