- Baik.

537
00:46:26,956 --> 00:46:28,166
Anda bisa membuka mata?

538
00:46:28,249 --> 00:46:30,376
Beri tahu aku jika terasa sakit.

539
00:46:31,586 --> 00:46:32,545
Baik.

540
00:46:37,675 --> 00:46:39,427
- Sedot cairan abdomen dahulu.
- Baik.

541
00:46:50,230 --> 00:46:51,564
- Masuk?
