568
00:50:32,160 --> 00:50:33,202
Bagaimana lagi?

569
00:50:34,036 --> 00:50:35,705
Kami harus menjalani hidup sendiri.

570
00:50:39,208 --> 00:50:40,251
Seon-woo.

571
00:50:42,879 --> 00:50:44,756
