tiga departemen ke sana

634
00:55:35,963 --> 00:55:38,340
tanpa memberitahumu apa-apa.

635
00:55:38,424 --> 00:55:41,594
Lalu kenapa mereka menghubungi
Direktur Sementara di pagi hari?

636
00:55:44,472 --> 00:55:45,806
Kemarin pagi...

637
00:55:46,974 --> 00:55:49,435
