638
00:55:52,313 --> 00:55:53,647
Kau tidak mampir...

639
00:55:54,982 --> 00:55:56,317
ke mana-mana.

640
00:55:59,487 --> 00:56:00,905
Kenapa kau berbohong?

641
00:56:02,239 --> 00:56:03,866
Omong kosong apa itu?

642
00:56:05,076 --> 00:56:06,577
Berani sekali kau mencurigaiku!

